{
  "stem": "24137.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember we were lying there, and it was just-- you know, it was a feeling that if you could describe one step before death.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But you just didn't know who's going to kill you, the Nazis or the sickness.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I just remember saying to the children, you know what?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you keep saying [HEBREW], then maybe it's like medicine, and maybe we'll get better.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we don't have a grown-up now to take care of us and give us medicine, so maybe now only God is going to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And maybe this is his medicine, that we're going to say this prayer, because we'll get the bread, but maybe that's not going to help us too much.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they brought us the bread, and I remember taking the bread and crumpling it up into tiny, tiny, tiny little crumbs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember when I was in Skawina, a little girl, I once saw a bird sitting in a tree and crying.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the bird was crying, crying, crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I saw another bigger bird came, and in their mouth, it has little crumbs of-- I don't know what it had-- it was putting it in the mouth of this other bird.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I remembered that in Bergen-Belsen, and I was thinking, if I have enough crumbs, maybe if I feed the children like a bird, a little, a little, a little, maybe it's gonna last us for a long time.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember I was doing that to all these little children, I mean, my cousins.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I don't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what I remember, seeing a lot of soldiers at the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] And it was the-- the British.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
